{"code": 0, "data": [{"cid": 807722, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Alice", "pid": 167371, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "首先要能毕业", "timestamp": 1609325645, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 807726, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Bob", "pid": 167371, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "Re Alice: 80%毕业不难吧", "timestamp": 1609325678, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 807727, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Alice", "pid": 167371, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "无系延毕退学率加起来已经十大几了", "timestamp": 1609325680, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 807733, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": true, "name": "洞主", "pid": 167371, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "Re Alice: 毕业还行，本校研肯定够不上了，还能在哪方面努努力啊", "timestamp": 1609325731, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 807746, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": true, "name": "洞主", "pid": 167371, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "外校推研要准备什么？或者有哪个组比较好进吗？", "timestamp": 1609325877, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 807756, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Carol", "pid": 167371, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "推研的话趁早联系老师，不仅是本校的，还有中科院，深研院等等\n至于毕业，毕业前把培养方案完成即可毕业。毕业之前不能有挂科且还没有补修的课。", "timestamp": 1609325939, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 807766, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": true, "name": "洞主", "pid": 167371, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "Re Carol: 谢谢C君!中科院的老师怎么接触啊？求指点", "timestamp": 1609326073, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 807774, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Dave", "pid": 167371, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "出国啊，分分钟吊打这些前几但是保研的", "timestamp": 1609326124, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 807779, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Eve", "pid": 167371, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "Re 洞主: 直球发邮件", "timestamp": 1609326160, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 807789, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": true, "name": "洞主", "pid": 167371, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "Re Eve: 就直接介绍自己什么的吗", "timestamp": 1609326246, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 807825, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Francis", "pid": 167371, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "Re 洞主: 说明来意，最好能看一些对方发过的论文，表达你对他研究方向的兴趣。中科院一般很欢迎清华的学生。", "timestamp": 1609326549, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 807860, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Carol", "pid": 167371, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "Re 洞主: 其实我也没经验。\n首先看看自己对哪个方向感兴趣，对中科院哪个所比较感兴趣（计算所，自动化所，空天院，声学所等等）。如果有感兴趣的老师或者实验室，可以打听一下老师的情况以及实验室具体研究方向（老师对于读博的影响还是很大的），最好能找到组内的同学问一下。此外，还要关注每个所的招生信息，有的是有夏令营，会确定一部分名额，有的是研究所举行面试，根据面试情况来确定录取名单。要与老师保持联系，注意观察老师是不是在养鱼，是否可能反悔，只有到了九月份走完了录取流程才算是真正推研成功。\n总之，如果想外推去中科院，要同时满足两个条件，一是拿到本校的外推资格，二是拿到中科院的录取资格。联系老师是为了让你拿到录取资格。", "timestamp": 1609326680, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 813340, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": true, "name": "洞主", "pid": 167371, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "Re Carol: 谢谢C君!", "timestamp": 1609407711, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 815332, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Carol", "pid": 167371, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "Re 洞主: 不用谢，有问题还可以继续问呀", "timestamp": 1609433900, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 1944614, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Grace", "pid": 167371, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "直接联系感兴趣的老师，无系毕业+找到自己喜欢的方向就是很不错了骚年！", "timestamp": 1624892200, "type": "text", "url": ""}], "post": {"deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "likenum": 22, "pid": 167371, "reply": 15, "tag": null, "text": "无系gpa 80％，怎么找条出路啊", "timestamp": 1609325593, "type": "text", "updated_at": 1624892202, "url": "", "vote": {}}}